Bing Russell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bing_Russell 0 Bing Russell (May 5, 1926 – April 8, 2003) was an American actor and Class A minor league baseball club owner. He is the father of Golden Globe Award-nominated actor Kurt Russell and grandfather of ex-major league baseball player Matt Franco.
